@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

actor "교사 (Teacher)" as T
actor "학생 (Student)" as S
actor "학부모 (Parent)" as P

rectangle "학생 관리 시스템 (Teacher ERP)" {
  usecase "성적 입력 및 수정" as UC_GradeManage
  usecase "성적 조회 (과목별/레이더차트)" as UC_GradeView
  usecase "학생부 유지보수\n(기본정보, 출결, 특기사항)" as UC_AcademicRecord
  usecase "피드백 작성 및 범위 설정" as UC_WriteFeedback
  usecase "교사 피드백 열람" as UC_ReadFeedback
  usecase "상담 내역 기록 및 교사간 공유" as UC_Counseling
  usecase "학생 기록 검색 및 필터링" as UC_Search
  usecase "보고서 생성 (PDF/Excel)" as UC_Report
  usecase "시스템 알림 수신" as UC_Notify
}

T --> UC_GradeManage
T --> UC_AcademicRecord
T --> UC_WriteFeedback
T --> UC_Counseling
T --> UC_Search
T --> UC_Report
T --> UC_Notify

S --> UC_GradeView
S --> UC_ReadFeedback
S --> UC_Notify

P --> UC_GradeView
P --> UC_ReadFeedback
P --> UC_Notify

' Use case relationships to show flow
UC_WriteFeedback ..> UC_ReadFeedback : "대상: 학생/학부모"
UC_GradeManage ..> UC_GradeView : "데이터 제공"

note top of T
  가르침 / 평가 / 상담
end note

note top of S
  성적 및 피드백 대상
end note

note top of P
  자녀 정보 조회
end note

@enduml
